## Recommended Action: `{{ risk.recommended_action }}`

| Action | Meaning |
|---|---|
| `sign` | Contract is acceptable as-is; proceed to signing. |
| `sign-with-changes` | Negotiate the listed items, then sign. |
| `legal-review-required` | Escalate to legal counsel before proceeding. |
| `do-not-sign` | Contract poses unacceptable risk; reject or renegotiate from scratch. |

